{"tid":28893,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日老細請食晏，90後新同事竟然唔比佢請","createTime":"2016-12-08T08:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T03:04:40.000Z","uid":33359,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7647df23842e2bbe97e601a9ba3684c0ea31e6f5","tid":28893,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"今日晏就老細無啦啦話去飲茶 我地唯有成公司八個人一齊去<br />\n咁去到酒樓都好地地 我個心一路都驚新同事嗌灌湯餃<br />\n好彩佢無咁做 <br />\n點知埋單個陣 老細話其實佢外匯賺左d 今日佢請<br />\n我地就梗係拍哂手掌多謝老細啦<br />\n點知新同事企起身話 我唔慣欠人野<br />\n一手拎左張單 再拎部iphone開個計數機係到禁<br />\n最尾除開一個人要比90.4 佢就拎左90.5比老細 <br />\n仲問老細有無一毫找返比佢<br />\n宜家d 90後真係<br />\n返到公司老細塊面仲黑過 B.B KING<br />\n我地班同事真係多得佢唔少"},{"pid":"ecdc655356450cfaa8f864922caedd3a79c32350","tid":28893,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304f638ffdd94dec50e0e7174d28de7669e507f7","tid":28893,"uid":20110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cef52ef78131f0bc1440ae1e4d5181df6d9840f","tid":28893,"uid":31310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"17aec58c83166349008f50e36f9325e9006300cc","tid":28893,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"一個i con都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cbb8ce01f3df5ac6b78f02fbe91365e40a6f24","tid":28893,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:42:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩老細專登出聲講說話我地聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話不如春茗都aa制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地班同事真係多得佢唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6967b68143995497a265f932c2f8e38e64fedaaa","tid":28893,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"